## Utilisation expéditive ⚫ Guide Rapide
## Rapid guide for expeditive use

A task can be done in two ways. Either by scanning specific sequence of barcodes (see the document) or by a combination of buttons ➀ and ➁. Button operations are preceded with symbol ●◯ for better readibility.

#### 2D Bluetooth Barcode Scanner
![CM-2D600 image](media/scanplan.jpg)

## Scan modes
### Switch between scan modes
> Transiter entre les modes
> 
●◯ Press ➀ until LED ➃ glows. Release the button. The LED ➃ blinks again while its color changed. The operating scan mode has switched - refer to the color list below to verify the scan mode.

Appuyer longuement sur ➀ pour basculer entre les modes d'operation. La couleur du LED ➃ indique le mode.

#### Color indicator ➃
* Blue: Mode BlueTooth
* Green: Mode USB
* Orange: Mode Memory

## Start scanning

Enabling **HID** mode transfers scanned data in a text editor window (notepad, word, gedit) or in a text box of a browser.
